Enum EISConstants.ParameterizedTestDataValueType

  • java.lang.Object

    EISConstants

    protected static enum EISConstants.ParameterizedTestDataValueType
extends java.lang.Enum<EISConstants.ParameterizedTestDataValueType>
    Test data types for use in declaring FieldData objects. They expect a delimited parameter representing the test data value.
    See Also:
    FieldData

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      VALUE
      Specifies that the parameter (if provided) is a literal value or a 'decorated' string. If no parameter is provided in the test properties file, it is expected that the test code will provide one.
      VALUE_CONSTANT
      Specifies that the parameter is the name of a constant in the test properties file.
